        "common_side_effect": "Nausea | Vomiting | Sore throat | Loss of appetite | Stomatitis (Inflammation of the mouth) | Hair loss | Low blood platelets | Rash | Fatigue | Anemia (low number of red blood cells) | Diarrhea | Decreased white blood cell count (neutrophils) | Neuropathy",
