        "qa": "Q. Is Pemsafe 500mg Injection a vesicant?::: No. Pemsafe 500mg Injection is not a vesicant.| Q. Is Pemsafe 500mg Injection safe?::: Pemsafe 500mg Injection is safe if used at prescribed doses for the prescribed duration as advised by your doctor.| Q. Does Pemsafe 500mg Injection cause hair loss?::: Yes. Pemsafe 500mg Injection is a prescription chemotherapy medication and hair loss is one of the possible side effects.",
