        "interaction": "Betagesic 650mg Tablet & Nimulid Syrup :  Concurrent use of Nimesulide and Paracetamol should be avoided. | Betagesic 650mg Tablet & Nised 50mg Syrup :  Concurrent use of Nimesulide and Paracetamol should be avoided. | Betagesic 650mg Tablet & Nise Tablet :  Concurrent use of Nimesulide and Paracetamol should be avoided. | Betagesic 650mg Tablet & Nimegesic Oral 50mg Suspension :  Concurrent use of Nimesulide and Paracetamol should be avoided. | Betagesic 650mg Tablet & Neemact 100mg Tablet MD :  Concurrent use of Nimesulide and Paracetamol should be avoided. | Betagesic 650mg Tablet & Nimlin MD 100mg Tablet :  Concurrent use of Nimesulide and Paracetamol should be avoided. | Betagesic 650mg Tablet & Nyci 100mg Tablet :  Concurrent use of Nimesulide and Paracetamol should be avoided. | Betagesic 650mg Tablet & Nimax 100mg Tablet :  Concurrent use of Nimesulide and Paracetamol should be avoided. | Betagesic 650mg Tablet & Nimax-MD 100mg Tablet :  Concurrent use of Nimesulide and Paracetamol should be avoided. | Betagesic 650mg Tablet & Nimcart 100mg Tablet MD :  Concurrent use of Nimesulide and Paracetamol should be avoided.",
