        "use_of": "Treatment of Gastroesophageal reflux disease (Acid reflux)|Treatment of Indigestion|Treatment of Gastritis",
        "common_side_effect": "Diarrhea | Stomach pain | Flatulence | Dryness in mouth | Dizziness | Headache",
